manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Industrial Table Lamps for Living Room

Innqoo-A Table Lamp Manufacturer Who Really Cares About Its Customers' Needs. As a 6-year old store, we have been committed to providing customers with the most suitable lighting fixtures. Over the past year we have introduced the Industrial Knob Desk Lamp which has been very popular with the public. But one customer told us that his mom with presbyopia couldn't easily find the switch late at night. We decided to take care of every customer's feelings and this upgraded touch table lamp was born! There is no need for any other operation, just gently touch our dimmable lamp and there are three levels of brightness for you to choose from~ 25% Low light is suitable as a night lamp to help you fall asleep. 60% Medium light provides a cosy glow that will enhances your dinner when paired with a dining table. 100% High Light is better choice for reading and working to protect your eyes.

3 In 1 Power for All We're keeping up with the changes and replacing the power strip with a multi-functional lamp that can also decorate your places. Plus, Plus, our upgraded USB-C port can charge more devices than the competition!!

Easy Start No other tools required,just few minutes you will be easy to assemble a bedroom lamp.You will enjoy this simple yet stylish bedside lamp right now! Thickened Glass Shade This clear lampshade is made of high-quality glass material. The durable glass shade with the lighting gives you an unrivalled sense of ambience Packing List The black lamps come with dual free LED bulbs,save your extra bulb cost.If there is any damage to the bedside lamps you receive，please reach out us on Amazon.We will try our best to help you solve problems！

Anti-skid Pad Weighted base with anti-slip pad to prevent slipping on smooth surfaces.It is very safe for people who have children or pets at home. TWO 6W T45 LED Bulbs The brightness is equivalent to 60W incandescent bulb. No flicker, can minimize the damage to eyes. The lifespan can be as long as 25,000Hrs. UL Listed Plug& Cord Safety first, all components of our touch lamp are UL approved.The 59" cable is long enough to reach a corner power outlet. Ideal Gift Widely used, this lamp is definitely a great gift choice for various festivals for all genders, young and old!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect little lamp
reviews.reviewText: These are the perfect little lamps for my living room. The design is aesthetic, it gives off the perfect amount of light (and has 3 settings to make it perfect), and I love the touch part of it. It has charging ports but I haven't used those yet. The shades are glass, but they were packed well and I got them all in one piece.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great buy! They look great and work well.
reviews.reviewText: These are great lights. They look nice and not cheap at all. The size is perfect. They aren't huge, but they are a perfect bedside table size. The touch to turn on and off is very handy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars These Are Perfect
reviews.reviewText: I purchased two of these for the nightstands in my bedroom, and they're great. They're the perfect size, and I love that you just have to tap them to turn them on, and then you can adjust the brightness by tapping them as well. Since the shade is glass, the lamp gives off a great amount of light when it's at the highest setting. I'd highly recommend these for their style and functionality.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect Night Stand Lamp
reviews.reviewText: These lamps are perfect for the bedroom. Quick and easy on/off with a touch of the base which also provides three levels of brightness to accommodate your needs and mood. Very easy to put together and stylish enough to fit any decor.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 13, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These are the coolest lamps I have ever owned, easy access plugs for chargers, very stylish, with a nice dim light for reading. One thing is that they are most definitely touch-powered. Touch them anywhere, the base, the rod, the very top, maybe even the bottom, I haven’t tried it yet, But touch it anywhere and it's on. The slightest graze will activate it, I find myself scrambling through the light cycle multiple times once it's accidentally triggered. Overall know I'm happy with my purchase in the long run

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Well made, very little assembly
reviews.reviewText: I was very happy with the workmanship on these lamps as well as how easy they were to finish assembly. Items were also packaged extremely well. They are not as large as I envisioned, and I did measure out my space, but the size is correct. Just one of those perception situations and can't put that on the seller.Saving seller for future reference.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I must say, the lamp adds a touch of elegance and sophistication to my room. Its soft glow illuminates the space and creates a cozy ambiance, making it my favorite spot to relax and unwind after a long day.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful lamps. Just what we were looking for.
reviews.reviewText: The bulbs that arrived with the lamps did not work. I reached out to the seller and they offered a bulb replacement refund. Once I received working bulbs, the lamps worked great. Very beautiful and perfect for our bedside.
